General.Name: Glory Forever PCL
General.Description: Glory Forever Public Company Limited operates an online media platform for digital books. It operates Kawebook.com, an online novel reading website; JINOVEL, an online reading-writing platform; and Alisa, a language models chatboat. The company also offers cyber security services and healthcare products, as well as services for virtual influencers. Glory Forever Public Company Limited was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Mueang Samut Sakhon, Thailand.
